A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: I have seen it twice now. The first time\, I would rank it just above the prequels. There were too many twists and unexpected outcomes to be truly enjoyable. However\, I enjoyed it much more the second time. Now I would rank it about equal with Return of the Jedi\, not quite as good as Rogue One or Empire Strikes Back\, but still an excellent movie.
